WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.988 align:middle line:90%


00:00:00.988 --> 00:00:04.446 align:middle line:90%
[LEAVES RUSTLING]

00:00:04.446 --> 00:00:07.410 align:middle line:90%
[INSTRUMENTAL MUSIC]

00:00:07.410 --> 00:00:15.830 align:middle line:90%


00:00:15.830 --> 00:00:17.580 align:middle line:90%
>> You said you'd sort this out.

00:00:17.580 --> 00:00:18.380 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:00:18.380 --> 00:00:19.180 align:middle line:90%
I'm going to.

00:00:19.180 --> 00:00:21.294 align:middle line:84%
>> You always leave
everything to me.

00:00:21.294 --> 00:00:24.140 align:middle line:90%


00:00:24.140 --> 00:00:25.376 align:middle line:90%
I haven't got time for this.

00:00:25.376 --> 00:00:26.500 align:middle line:90%
>> All you ever do is work.

00:00:26.500 --> 00:00:29.320 align:middle line:84%
>> (ANGRILY) Well,
somebody has to.

00:00:29.320 --> 00:00:31.226 align:middle line:90%
>> Hey, what's wrong?

00:00:31.226 --> 00:00:33.192 align:middle line:84%
(EXASPERATED) You
never let me touch you.

00:00:33.192 --> 00:00:34.650 align:middle line:84%
>> Do you even know
what day it is?

00:00:34.650 --> 00:00:39.610 align:middle line:90%


00:00:39.610 --> 00:00:42.586 align:middle line:90%
[CELL PHONE RINGING]

00:00:42.586 --> 00:00:46.080 align:middle line:90%


00:00:46.080 --> 00:00:49.825 align:middle line:84%
Do we have to talk
about this now?

00:00:49.825 --> 00:00:51.813 align:middle line:90%
I'm by the woods.

00:00:51.813 --> 00:00:54.298 align:middle line:90%
(ANGRILY) You do.

00:00:54.298 --> 00:00:56.286 align:middle line:90%
I'm sick of it.

00:00:56.286 --> 00:00:58.290 align:middle line:90%
It's like living with a big kid.

00:00:58.290 --> 00:01:02.100 align:middle line:90%
No, Mark, it's not OK.

00:01:02.100 --> 00:01:05.070 align:middle line:90%
Well, I've had enough.

00:01:05.070 --> 00:01:07.050 align:middle line:90%
Really, I can't do it anymore.

00:01:07.050 --> 00:01:11.010 align:middle line:90%


00:01:11.010 --> 00:01:13.980 align:middle line:90%
For God's sake.

00:01:13.980 --> 00:01:16.455 align:middle line:90%
But it's all the time.

00:01:16.455 --> 00:01:18.460 align:middle line:90%
Yes, you do.

00:01:18.460 --> 00:01:19.330 align:middle line:90%
I think this is it.

00:01:19.330 --> 00:01:21.760 align:middle line:90%


00:01:21.760 --> 00:01:22.560 align:middle line:90%
It's over.

00:01:22.560 --> 00:01:25.836 align:middle line:90%


00:01:25.836 --> 00:01:27.240 align:middle line:90%
Hello?

00:01:27.240 --> 00:01:30.424 align:middle line:90%
(EXASPERATED) Oh, dammit.

00:01:30.424 --> 00:01:33.812 align:middle line:90%
[BIRDS CHIRPING, CROW CAWING]

00:01:33.812 --> 00:01:35.748 align:middle line:90%


00:01:35.748 --> 00:01:37.570 align:middle line:84%
Oh, bloody piece of
plastic shitwank.

00:01:37.570 --> 00:01:40.755 align:middle line:90%


00:01:40.755 --> 00:01:42.240 align:middle line:90%
Sorry.

00:01:42.240 --> 00:01:44.202 align:middle line:90%
I hope you didn't hear all that.

00:01:44.202 --> 00:01:46.211 align:middle line:90%
>> Plastic shitwank?

00:01:46.211 --> 00:01:47.133 align:middle line:90%
Not all of it.

00:01:47.133 --> 00:01:49.899 align:middle line:90%


00:01:49.899 --> 00:01:51.100 align:middle line:90%
Are you lost, dear?

00:01:51.100 --> 00:01:51.900 align:middle line:90%
>> No, no.

00:01:51.900 --> 00:01:55.071 align:middle line:84%
I've just parked by
the road somewhere.

00:01:55.071 --> 00:01:57.116 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, don't worry.

00:01:57.116 --> 00:01:59.130 align:middle line:90%
I'll show you the way.

00:01:59.130 --> 00:01:59.930 align:middle line:90%
Come on.

00:01:59.930 --> 00:02:13.040 align:middle line:90%


00:02:13.040 --> 00:02:15.060 align:middle line:84%
>> You're sure this
is the right way?

00:02:15.060 --> 00:02:16.090 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, yes.

00:02:16.090 --> 00:02:19.118 align:middle line:90%
I know this wood intimately.

00:02:19.118 --> 00:02:23.660 align:middle line:90%
Ah, here's my old friend.

00:02:23.660 --> 00:02:25.350 align:middle line:90%
>> A tree?

00:02:25.350 --> 00:02:29.730 align:middle line:90%
>> An elder, like me.

00:02:29.730 --> 00:02:30.660 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:02:30.660 --> 00:02:33.330 align:middle line:90%
Well, I have to go.

00:02:33.330 --> 00:02:34.350 align:middle line:90%
>> What's the rush?

00:02:34.350 --> 00:02:35.780 align:middle line:90%
>> I have to get back.

00:02:35.780 --> 00:02:38.880 align:middle line:84%
>> But it's such
a beautiful day.

00:02:38.880 --> 00:02:42.150 align:middle line:84%
Just let's sit
here for a minute,

00:02:42.150 --> 00:02:44.688 align:middle line:90%
and then we can find the car.

00:02:44.688 --> 00:03:01.170 align:middle line:90%


00:03:01.170 --> 00:03:05.230 align:middle line:84%
Made from the flowers
of this very tree.

00:03:05.230 --> 00:03:09.214 align:middle line:90%


00:03:09.214 --> 00:03:11.320 align:middle line:90%
[CHUCKLES]

00:03:11.320 --> 00:03:12.120 align:middle line:90%
To you, my dear.

00:03:12.120 --> 00:03:21.030 align:middle line:90%


00:03:21.030 --> 00:03:23.390 align:middle line:90%
>> It's really nice.

00:03:23.390 --> 00:03:24.920 align:middle line:90%
You made it from these?

00:03:24.920 --> 00:03:25.790 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, yes.

00:03:25.790 --> 00:03:29.750 align:middle line:84%
The elder is a very
magical tree, isn't it?

00:03:29.750 --> 00:03:32.570 align:middle line:84%
She gives so many
cures, they used

00:03:32.570 --> 00:03:35.670 align:middle line:90%
to call her the medicine chest.

00:03:35.670 --> 00:03:38.505 align:middle line:84%
But It was bad luck to
use her in a bonfire.

00:03:38.505 --> 00:03:41.370 align:middle line:90%


00:03:41.370 --> 00:03:44.890 align:middle line:90%
(SOFTLY) Elder be lady's tree.

00:03:44.890 --> 00:03:48.960 align:middle line:84%
Burn her not, or
cursed you'll be.

00:03:48.960 --> 00:03:51.780 align:middle line:90%
>> We won't get cursed for this?

00:03:51.780 --> 00:03:53.390 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh no.

00:03:53.390 --> 00:03:55.355 align:middle line:90%
She approves of this.

00:03:55.355 --> 00:03:59.070 align:middle line:90%
Don't you, old girl?

00:03:59.070 --> 00:04:02.760 align:middle line:84%
>> I really have
to find the car.

00:04:02.760 --> 00:04:05.304 align:middle line:84%
>> It will still be
there in a minute or two.

00:04:05.304 --> 00:04:08.748 align:middle line:90%
[GLASSES CLINKING]

00:04:08.748 --> 00:04:10.884 align:middle line:90%


00:04:10.884 --> 00:04:12.425 align:middle line:84%
>> So did you come
here for a picnic?

00:04:12.425 --> 00:04:18.019 align:middle line:90%


00:04:18.019 --> 00:04:20.750 align:middle line:90%
>> I come here every year--

00:04:20.750 --> 00:04:22.438 align:middle line:90%
my wedding anniversary.

00:04:22.438 --> 00:04:26.182 align:middle line:90%


00:04:26.182 --> 00:04:29.700 align:middle line:84%
Look what my husband
left here many moons ago.

00:04:29.700 --> 00:04:33.560 align:middle line:90%


00:04:33.560 --> 00:04:35.790 align:middle line:90%
>> It's my anniversary too--

00:04:35.790 --> 00:04:37.107 align:middle line:90%
five years.

00:04:37.107 --> 00:04:38.540 align:middle line:90%
>> Hmm.

00:04:38.540 --> 00:04:40.770 align:middle line:90%
>> I think it'll be my last.

00:04:40.770 --> 00:04:44.260 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, you'll work it out.

00:04:44.260 --> 00:04:45.520 align:middle line:90%
>> I don't think so.

00:04:45.520 --> 00:04:51.520 align:middle line:90%


00:04:51.520 --> 00:04:53.450 align:middle line:90%
So where's your husband?

00:04:53.450 --> 00:04:56.380 align:middle line:90%
Oh, sorry.

00:04:56.380 --> 00:04:58.290 align:middle line:90%
>> Don't be.

00:04:58.290 --> 00:05:02.085 align:middle line:84%
We had 43 years together and
three beautiful children.

00:05:02.085 --> 00:05:05.160 align:middle line:90%


00:05:05.160 --> 00:05:08.910 align:middle line:84%
Yes, love can be
painful at times,

00:05:08.910 --> 00:05:11.210 align:middle line:84%
but it's still the
greatest show on Earth.

00:05:11.210 --> 00:05:15.090 align:middle line:90%


00:05:15.090 --> 00:05:17.640 align:middle line:90%
>> That's a beautiful shawl.

00:05:17.640 --> 00:05:18.440 align:middle line:90%
>> Fairly old now.

00:05:18.440 --> 00:05:21.926 align:middle line:90%


00:05:21.926 --> 00:05:24.914 align:middle line:90%
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

00:05:24.914 --> 00:05:28.900 align:middle line:90%


00:05:28.900 --> 00:05:35.930 align:middle line:84%
It will be dark soon,
the time for lovers.

00:05:35.930 --> 00:05:36.730 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh my god.

00:05:36.730 --> 00:05:39.560 align:middle line:90%
It's so late.

00:05:39.560 --> 00:05:41.810 align:middle line:84%
I thought we'd
only just arrived.

00:05:41.810 --> 00:05:45.290 align:middle line:84%
>> Time does funny
things around here.

00:05:45.290 --> 00:05:47.110 align:middle line:90%
>> I really have to go.

00:05:47.110 --> 00:05:48.650 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, of course.

00:05:48.650 --> 00:05:51.350 align:middle line:90%


00:05:51.350 --> 00:05:53.090 align:middle line:84%
Just follow the
path straight on.

00:05:53.090 --> 00:05:55.470 align:middle line:90%
You'll find it.

00:05:55.470 --> 00:05:56.270 align:middle line:90%
>> Thank you.

00:05:56.270 --> 00:06:01.010 align:middle line:90%


00:06:01.010 --> 00:06:03.686 align:middle line:84%
I hope to see you
again sometime.

00:06:03.686 --> 00:06:04.560 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh you will, dear.

00:06:04.560 --> 00:06:14.650 align:middle line:90%


00:06:14.650 --> 00:06:17.225 align:middle line:90%
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

00:06:17.225 --> 00:06:37.552 align:middle line:90%


00:06:37.552 --> 00:06:40.905 align:middle line:90%
[LEAVES RUSTLING]

00:06:40.905 --> 00:06:43.600 align:middle line:90%


00:06:43.600 --> 00:06:44.400 align:middle line:90%
>> There you are.

00:06:44.400 --> 00:06:48.152 align:middle line:90%


00:06:48.152 --> 00:06:51.370 align:middle line:84%
You got cut off, and then
I've been looking for ages,

00:06:51.370 --> 00:06:54.100 align:middle line:84%
and I find the car,
and you're not in it.

00:06:54.100 --> 00:06:58.880 align:middle line:84%
>> Sorry, and I'm sorry
for how I've been.

00:06:58.880 --> 00:06:59.680 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, me too.

00:06:59.680 --> 00:07:02.380 align:middle line:90%


00:07:02.380 --> 00:07:05.270 align:middle line:84%
You rushed off before
I could give you this.

00:07:05.270 --> 00:07:08.080 align:middle line:90%
Happy anniversary.

00:07:08.080 --> 00:07:09.364 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh my god.

00:07:09.364 --> 00:07:12.703 align:middle line:90%


00:07:12.703 --> 00:07:15.100 align:middle line:90%
>> Is that good or bad?

00:07:15.100 --> 00:07:19.600 align:middle line:84%
>> It's the same as this
lady I just met has.

00:07:19.600 --> 00:07:20.789 align:middle line:90%
We'd better show her.

00:07:20.789 --> 00:07:21.589 align:middle line:90%
Come on.

00:07:21.589 --> 00:07:25.380 align:middle line:90%


00:07:25.380 --> 00:07:26.680 align:middle line:90%
She's gone.

00:07:26.680 --> 00:07:27.960 align:middle line:90%
>> Are you sure it was here?

00:07:27.960 --> 00:07:28.760 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, yeah.

00:07:28.760 --> 00:07:30.200 align:middle line:90%
It had a-- oh.

00:07:30.200 --> 00:07:39.910 align:middle line:90%


00:07:39.910 --> 00:07:42.470 align:middle line:90%
[GASPS]

00:07:42.470 --> 00:07:43.890 align:middle line:90%


00:07:43.890 --> 00:07:44.986 align:middle line:90%
>> What?

00:07:44.986 --> 00:07:47.710 align:middle line:90%


00:07:47.710 --> 00:07:49.480 align:middle line:84%
>> Time does funny
things around here.

00:07:49.480 --> 00:08:23.380 align:middle line:90%


00:08:23.380 --> 00:08:26.430 align:middle line:90%
[SOOTHING MUSIC]

00:08:26.430 --> 00:09:29.344 align:middle line:90%